{"tid":1548991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲大家用各種方式發出不自殺聲明","createTime":"2019-09-07T07:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T08:08:21.000Z","uid":36111,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf1e8829840e046fb5c1a6e0c1a4eea587ebd6c","tid":1548991,"uid":36111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"嚟到九月七日嘅香港，每日都有好多唔同浮屍、自殺嘅case。<br />\n<br />\n手足隨時<span style=\"color: red;\">被自殺</span>，死於非命。希望大家都可以用各種方式講明自己唔會<span style=\"color: red;\">自殺</span>。最好同多d人講，唔限於身邊親友，因為我地唔再知殺人政權可以做d嘢。<br />\n<br />\n例如轉cover photo，將自己唔會輕生嘅宣言同哂全世界講。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oj7bLD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOj7bLD7.png&h=eb5b5c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光後香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人要贏</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2af68564deeb4cd8d87d9fe2ad4836783c04ad0","tid":1548991,"uid":36111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0543de6b3ccb77c0fe811466347e0e18a6928b93","tid":1548991,"uid":36111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:30:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67cc04d441fface70fe36d533dd2c71fc9f54861","tid":1548991,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEQwLSq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEQwLSq.png&h=e86155e1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}